17:T8cc6,<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Have you ever noticed how much is going on with a cereal box? From the bright colors and big letters to the fun characters,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">cereal boxes</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>are made to grab our attention. But why do cereal companies spend so much time on these little cardboard boxes? Let’s take a closer look at these boxes to understand why they look the way they do and what makes them special.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The main job of a cereal box is to hold the cereal, but it does more than that. The box acts like a small advertisement to catch your eye and make you want to buy that cereal. When you're in the store, there are so many options, and each brand wants you to pick their box over the others. That’s why the design of the box is so important for helping each brand stand out.</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.7rem !important; font-weight: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">How tall is the Average Cereal Box?</strong></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The height of a cereal box can vary depending on the brand and type of cereal, but most standard<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://umbrellapackaging.com/cereal-packaging-boxes/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(68, 64, 230) !important; text-decoration: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">cereal boxes</strong></a><span>&nbsp;</span>are about<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">10 to 12 inches</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>tall. This is roughly the same height as a standard dinner plate. Some smaller boxes, like those for single servings or snacks, can be shorter, around<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">7 to 9 inches</strong>. Larger or family-sized boxes may be taller or have a slightly different shape, but they usually fall within the same range.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Here are the types of these boxes based on size:</p><table style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px !important; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid gray !important; text-indent: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: oklch(0.373 0.034 259.733); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; width: 736px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Type of Cereal Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></strong></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Typical Size<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></strong></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Use<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></strong></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">Single-Serve Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">1 ounce (28g)<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">For individual servings, portable, and convenient for on-the-go<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">Regular-Sized Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">12 to 16 ounces (340-450g)<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">Standard size for everyday household use.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">Family-Sized Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">18 to 24 ounces (510-680g)<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">Larger size for families or frequent cereal eaters, offering more value.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">Bulk/Economy-Sized Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">30 ounces (850g) or more<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.07) !important;">Extra-large for bulk purchases, best for large households or cost savings.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 170.766px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">Mini Cereal Box<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 172.578px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">1 ounce (28g)<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td><td style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 15px !important; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5); width: 391.656px; font-size: 14px !important; background-color: white !important;">Small, often part of variety packs, perfect for trying different flavors.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">So, in general, cereal boxes are tall enough to stand upright on a shelf but not so tall that they are difficult to store.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img src="https://umbrellapackaging.com/images/How%20tall%20is%20the%20Average%20Cereal%20Box.webp" alt="How tall is the Average Cereal Box" loading="lazy" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; display: block; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 736px;"></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.7rem !important; font-weight: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Designing Your Cereal Packaging Boxes the Right Way</strong></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Creating a cereal box that stands out on the shelf is important for attracting buyers and building brand loyalty. Here’s a simple guide on how to design an effective cereal box:</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Choose the Right Colors</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Colors are powerful! Bright colors like red, yellow, and blue catch the eye and create excitement. Use colors that match the vibe you want for your cereal. For example:</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Kids' Cereal boxes are Go for fun, vibrant colors like red, orange, and blue.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Healthy Cereal boxes use calming colors like green or brown, which can make the cereal feel more natural and nutritious.</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Add a Fun Character</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">A friendly character in your cereal box can make it more appealing, especially for kids. Think of famous cereal mascots like Tony the Tiger. Kids feel a connection with these characters, making them excited to choose that cereal. Even for adult cereals, a simple logo or nature-based image can create a good vibe.</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Make the Brand Name Stand Out</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Your cereal name should be big, bold, and easy to read from a distance. This helps customers recognize it quickly, especially if they're already familiar with your brand. Use a font that suits the cereal's style. For example, a playful font works for kids' cereals, while a clean, simple font is better for healthier cereals.</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Highlight Key Benefits</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Adding phrases like “Whole Grain,” “High in Fiber,” or “Gluten-Free” on the front of the box can catch the eye of health-conscious buyers. Showing these main benefits on the front makes it clear why people should pick your cereal instead of others<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">.</strong></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Make the Back of the Box Interesting</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The back of the box is where you can add more personality. For kids' cereals, include games, puzzles, or fun facts to keep them entertained. For adult cereals, share tips on healthy eating, recipes, or a story about the brand.</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Consider Eco-Friendly Packaging</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Using recycled or<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://umbrellapackaging.com/boxes-by-material/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(68, 64, 230) !important; text-decoration: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">eco-friendly materials</strong></a><span>&nbsp;</span>can attract environmentally conscious buyers. Promoting this on the box (with words like “Made with Recycled Materials” or “100% Biodegradable”) shows that your brand cares about the environment, which is a big plus for many consumers.</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 9px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.5rem !important; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; opacity: 0.9; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Keep the Size Just Right</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Your box should be big enough to hold the cereal safely but not so big that it seems half-empty. A well-sized box gives a feeling of value and trustworthiness, while oversized boxes can disappoint customers.</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.7rem !important; font-weight: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">What Are Cereal Boxes Made Of?</strong></h2>15:["$","div",null,{"className":"sm:max-w-8xl max-w-[95%] mx-auto py-12 md:py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 lg:gap-16","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full lg:w-2/3","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"blog_content bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-gray-100","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg    [&_h1]:text-3xl [&_h1]:md:text-4xl [&_h1]:font-bold [&_h1]:text-[#213554] [&_h1]:mt-10 [&_h1]:mb-6   [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:md:text-3xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-[#213554] [&_h2]:mt-8 [&_h2]:mb-4   [&_h3]:text-xl [&_h3]:md:text-2xl [&_h3]:font-bold [&_h3]:text-[#213554] [&_h3]:mt-6 [&_h3]:mb-3   [&_p]:mb-6 [&_p]:leading-8   [&_a]:text-[#EE334B] [&_a]:font-bold [&_a]:no-underline [&_a:hover]:underline   [&_strong]:text-[#213554] [&_strong]:font-bold   [&_img]:rounded-3xl [&_img]:shadow-xl [&_img]:my-10 [&_img]:w-full [&_img]:h-auto   [&_blockquote]:border-l-4 [&_blockquote]:border-[#EE334B] [&_blockquote]:pl-6 [&_blockquote]:pr-6 [&_blockquote]:py-4 [&_blockquote]:italic [&_blockquote]:bg-gray-50 [&_blockquote]:rounded-r-2xl [&_blockquote]:my-8   [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-8 [&_ul]:mb-6 [&_ul]:space-y-3   [&_ol]:list-decimal [&_ol]:ml-8 [&_ol]:mb-6 [&_ol]:space-y-3   [&_li]:leading-8","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$17"}}]}],"$L18"]}],"$L19"]}]}]
