23:T136e,<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">n printing, CMYK stands for<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Cyan, Magenta, Yellow, and Key (Black),</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>which are the four primary ink colors used in color printing. This color model is called the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">Subtractive Color Model</strong>, meaning colors are created by removing brightness from a white background.</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 1.7rem !important; font-weight: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-weight: bolder;">CMYK Explained:<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://umbrellapackaging.com/" target="_blank" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(68, 64, 230) !important; text-decoration: inherit; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;">The Go-To Color Model in Professional Printing</a></strong></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid;"></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 8px !important; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important; font-size: medium; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacin